Project Outcome
This project demonstrates practical experience in information gathering, enumeration, OSINT, and vulnerability assessment techniques commonly used during the reconnaissance phase of penetration testing engagements.

Disclaimer
This project was conducted in a controlled laboratory environment for educational and ethical cybersecurity training purposes only.
